v.com%2Fscience%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-boeing-starliner-that-will-take-sunita-williams-into-space-a-third-time-5602094%5C%22%3EBoeing%20Starliner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20set%20to%20take%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%20to%20space%20for%20a%20third%20time%2C%20has%20been%20postponed%20due%20to%20a%20technical%20glitch.%20No%20new%20date%20has%20been%20announced%20for%20the%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%2C%20poster%20girl%20for%20women%20aspiring%20to%20fly%20into%20space%2C%20was%20set%20to%20reach%20for%20the%20skies%20again%20today%20in%20a%20brand-new%20spacecraft.%20The%20Boeing%20Starliner%20was%20set%20to%20lift%20off%20from%20the%20Kennedy%20Space%20Center%20in%20Florida's%20Cape%20Canaveral%20at%208.04%20am%20India%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20just%2090%20minutes%20before%20the%20lift-off%2C%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Atlas%20V%20rocket%20was%20called%20off.%20US%20space%20agency%20NASA%20has%20announced%20there%20was%20an%20off-nominal%20condition%20on%20an%20oxygen%20relief%20valve%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20postponement.%20Ms%20Williams%20and%20NASA's%20Barry%20Wilmore%2C%20who%20were%20to%20fly%20the%20Starliner%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20have%20safely%20exited%20the%20spacecraft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fwhy-sunita-williams-named-starliner-spacecraft-calypso-for-space-mission-5601441%5C%22%3EWhy%20Sunita%20Williams%20Named%20Starliner%20Spacecraft%20'Calypso'%20For%20Space%20Mission%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20have%20been%20the%20third%20space%20travel%20for%20the%20Indian-origin%20astronaut%2C%20who%20has%20already%20spent%20322%20days%20in%20space%20and%20held%20a%20record%20for%20the%20maximum%20hours%20of%20spacewalk%20by%20a%20woman%2C%20before%20being%20overtaken%20by%20Peggy%20Whitson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20she%20would%20have%20made%20history%20as%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20fly%20on%20a%20maiden%20crewed%20mission%20of%20a%20new%20space%20shuttle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%20went%20on%20her%20first%20space%20voyage%20on%20December%209%2C%202006%2C%20which%20lasted%20till%20June%2022%2C%202007.%20While%20onboard%2C%20she%20established%20a%20world%20record%20for%20women%20by%20going%20on%20four%20spacewalks%20that%20added%20up%20to%2029%20hours%20and%2017%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20second%20voyage%20was%20from%20July%2014%20to%20November%2018%2C%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fwhat-sunita-williams-carries-to-space-as-her-lucky-charm-5600710%5C%22%3EGanesh%20Idol%2C%20Bhagwad%20Gita%3A%20What%20Sunita%20Williams%20Takes%20To%20Space%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2059-year-old%20admitted%20to%20being%20a%20bit%20nervous%20but%20said%20she%20had%20no%20jitters%20about%20flying%20in%20a%20new%20spacecraft.%20She%20had%20helped%20design%20the%20Starliner%2C%20working%20with%20engineers%20from%20NASA%20and%20Boeing.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20reach%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20it%20will%20be%20like%20going%20back%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20flight%2C%20she%20had%20told%20NDTV%20that%20she%20intended%20to%20carry%20an%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ganesh%20on%20this%20journey%2C%20since%20he%20is%20her%20%26quot%3Bgood%20luck%20charm%26quot%3B.%20Earlier%2C%20she%20had%20carried%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Bhagwad%20Gita.%20An%20enthusiastic%20marathoner%2C%20she%20had%20even%20completed%20a%20triathlon%20in%20space%2C%20competing%20with%20athletes%20back%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010-day%20mission%20will%20help%20the%20Starliner%20prove%20its%20space-worthiness.%20It%20would%20also%20prove%20the%20team's%20readiness%20to%20achieve%20NASA%20certification%20and%20fly%20long-duration%20missions%20for%20the%20US%20space%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C