2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20India%20all-rounder%20has%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism%20-%20both%20as%20player%20and%20captain.%20Hardik%20completed%20a%20sensational%20trade%20to%20Mumbai%20Indians%20from%20Gujarat%20Titans%20ahead%20of%20the%20season%20and%20was%20appointed%20captain%20of%20the%20franchise.%20It%20meant%20that%20he%20ended%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E's%20ten-year%20tenure%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20MI%20-%20a%20decision%20that%20was%20not%20accepted%20well%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20fanbase.%20Things%20got%20worse%20as%20the%20team%20did%20not%20perform%20well%20on%20the%20field%20and%20they%20are%20currently%20last%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20points%20table%20with%20just%20three%20victories.%20Hardik%20recently%20opened%20up%20about%20his%20turbulent%20journey%20in%20this%20year's%20competition%20and%20namedropped%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20making%20his%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResponsibility-wise%2C%20I%20was%20always%20someone%20who%20wanted%20responsibilty%20because%20when%20you%20own%20your%20things%2C%20it%20kind%20of%20becomes%20more%20personal%20to%20you.%20So%20for%20me%2C%20it%20was%20always%20about%20owning%20my%20mistake%20and%20at%20the%20same%20point%20of%20time%20taking%20those%20chances%2C%20maybe%20failing%20and%20learning.%20That%20experience%20no%20one%20can%20teach%20you%20-%20not%20your%20closest%20aide%2C%20not%20your%20idol%2C%20to%20some%20extent%20not%20even%20Mahi%20Bhai%20(MS%20Dhoni)%20when%20he%20was%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20Hardik%20told%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMI's%20latest%20defeat%20came%20against%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20and%20Hardik%20was%20quite%20critical%20of%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20that%20will%20take%20time%20to%20answer.%20But%20for%20now%2C%20not%20much%20to%20say.%20Obviously%2C%20we%20couldn't%20form%20partnerships%20and%20kept%20losing%20wickets.%20Bowlers%20did%20a%20fantastic%20job%20on%20this%20track%2C%26quot%3B%20Pandya%20said%20after%20his%20team%20failed%20to%20score%20170%2C%20losing%20to%20KKR%20at%20home%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2012%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20all-rounder%20did%20try%20to%20motivate%20his%20side%20to%20finish%20strong%20after%20a%20rather%20disappointing%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20keep%20fighting%2C%20that's%20what%20I%20keep%20telling%20myself.%20It's%20challenging%2C%20but%20you%20take%20the%20challenges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715046360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fvlgmu62o_hardik-pandya-bcci_625x300_07_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fnot-even-mahi-bhai-can-teach-hardik-pandya-namedrops-ms-dhoni-in-huge-remark-5600666%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20has%20been%20a%20disappointing%20IPL%202024%20campaign%20for%20Hardik%20Pandya%20as%20the%20India%20all-rounder%20has%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism%20-%20both%20as%20player%20and%20captain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mama%20vs%20Dada%2C%20Cricketer's%20Debut%2C%20Family%20Feud%3A%20Key%20Battles%20In%203rd%20Phase%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMama%20vs%20Dada%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20a%20cricketer%20making%20his%20poll%20debut%20against%20a%20political%20veteran%20in%20West%20Bengal%20-%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20today%20will%20encompass%2095%20constituencies%20spread%20across%2011%20states.%20The%20Betul%20constituency%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20originally%20slated%20for%20Phase%202%2C%20has%20been%20rescheduled%20for%20Phase%203%20due%20to%20the%20death%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20candidate.%20All%2026%20constituencies%20of%20Gujarat%20will%20cast%20their%20votes%20in%20a%20single%20phase%2C%20along%20with%20two%20constituencies%20in%20Goa.%20The%20remaining%2014%20constituencies%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20predominantly%20situated%20in%20north%20Karnataka%2C%20are%20also%20scheduled%20for%20polling%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20marking%20the%20conclusion%20of%20voting%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAhead%20of%20the%20polls%2C%20here%20is%20a%20look%20at%20some%20of%20the%20key%20battles%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGandhinagar%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20vs%20Sonal%20Patel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgandhinagar-lok-sabha-constituency-a-bjp-stronghold-with-notable-leaders-5175061%5C%22%3EGandhinagar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20is%20a%20key%20stronghold%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Since%201989%2C%20it%20has%20consistently%20delivered%20victories%20to%20the%20party%2C%20spanning%20six%20terms%20for%20BJP%20veteran%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%20and%2C%20and%20most%20recently%20in%202019%2C%20for%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20secured%20a%20comprehensive%20win%20by%20over%205%20lakh%20votes.%20As%20the%20elections%20approach%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20faces%20Congress%20candidate%20Sonal%20Patel%2C%20aiming%20to%20maintain%20the%20constituency's%20allegiance%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMainpuri%3A%20Dimple%20Yadav%20vs%20Jaiveer%20Singh%20vs%20Shiv%20Prasad%20Yadav%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incumbent%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-2024-mainpuri-mulayam-singhs-stronghold-samajwadi-party-dominant-since-1996-5269981%5C%22%3EMainpuri%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0MP%2C%20Dimple%20Yadav%2C%20faces%20a%20formidable%20opponent%20in%20Jaiveer%20Singh%20of%20the%20BJP.%20While%20initially%20perceived%20as%20a%20head-to-head%20battle%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20Shiv%20Prasad%20Yadav%20from%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20has%20presented%20a%20third%20contender.%20Dimple%20Yadav%2C%20who%20clinched%20Mainpuri%20in%20a%20bypoll%20following%20the%20death%20of%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20in%202022%2C%20secured%20victory%20with%20a%20surge%20of%20sympathy%20votes.%20This%20upcoming%20election%20poses%20as%20the%20primary%20litmus%20test%20for%20her.%20In%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20contest%20was%20confined%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20SP%2C%20with%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20emerging%20victorious%20against%20BJP's%20Prem%20Singh%20Shakya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBaramati%3A%20Supriya%20Sule%20vs%20Sunetra%20Pawar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaramati-lok-sabha-election-family-feud-in-baramati-potential-supriya-sule-sunetra-pawar-battle-5307631%5C%22%3EBaramati%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20fixed%20on%20the%20Pawar%20family%20rift%20as%20the%20stage%20is%20being%20readied%20for%20a%20clash%20between%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20representing%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20NCP%2C%20and%20her%20cousin%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20wife%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20the%20NCP%20candidate.%20Since%202009%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20daughter%20and%20the%20incumbent%20MP%2C%20has%20consistently%20won%20in%20this%20constituency.%20Baramati%20has%20long%20been%20a%20stronghold%20of%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20his%20tenure%20as%20an%20MLA%20in%201967.%20Throughout%20subsequent%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20candidates%20backed%20by%20him%20have%20emerged%20victorious%20in%20Baramati%2C%20including%20Ajit%20in%201991.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20himself%20held%20the%20parliamentary%20seat%20from%201996%20until%20Supriya%20succeeded%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShivamogga%3A%20BY%20Raghavendra%20vs%20Geetha%20Shivarajkumar%20vs%20KS%20Eshwarappa%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-shimoga-ex-chief-ministers-children-bjp-rebel-to-battle-for-this-karnataka-seat-5595861%5C%22%3EShivamogga%3C%2Fa%3E%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20KS%20Eshwarappa%2C%20the%20suspended%20BJP%20leader%20has%20announced%20his%20intention%20to%20run%20as%20an%20independent%20candidate%2C%20challenging%20the%20incumbent%20MP%2C%20BY%20Raghavendra%2C%20son%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20BS%20Yediyurappa%2C%20and%20Geetha%20Shivrajkumar%2C%20the%20Congress%20candidate%2C%20spouse%20of%20Kannada%20superstar%20Shiva%20Rajkumar%20and%20daughter%20of%20another%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Sarekoppa%20Bangarappa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20parliamentary%20area%2C%20consisting%20of%20eight%20assembly%20segments%2C%20has%20been%20firmly%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Yediyurappa%20family%20since%202009.%20In%20the%202009%20general%20elections%2C%20BY%20Raghavendra%20secured%20victory%20with%20a%20margin%20of%20over%204.82%20lakh%20votes%20and%20a%20vote%20share%20of%2050.58%20per%20cent.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20relinquished%20the%20seat%20to%20his%20father%2C%20BS%20Yediyurappa%2C%20who%20triumphed%20with%20a%20commanding%20lead%20of%20over%206%20lakh%20votes%20and%20a%2053.69%20per%20cent%20vote%20share.%20Returning%20to%20Raghavendra%20in%202019%2C%20he%20secured%20a%20landslide%20victory%20with%20over%207.29%20lakh%20votes%20and%20a%20vote%20share%20of%2056.86%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBerhampore%3A%20Yusuf%20Pathan%20vs%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBerhampore%20in%20West%20Bengal%20has%20long%20been%20a%20stronghold%20for%20the%20Congress%20party.%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20the%20current%20M