0aftermath%20of%20a%20near-catastrophic%20Alaska%20Airlines%20flight%20in%20January%20in%20which%20a%20panel%20on%20the%20fuselage%20blew%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FAA%20has%20given%20the%20company%20three%20months%20to%20present%20a%20plan%20to%20address%20%26quot%3Bsystemic%20quality-control%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing's%20management%20of%20the%20787%20came%20under%20question%20at%20an%20April%2017%20Senate%20hearing%20at%20which%20a%20company%20whistleblower%20testified%20that%20he%20was%20retaliated%20against%20after%20raising%20questions%20about%20manufacturing%20processes%20on%20the%20787%20that%20he%20believed%20threaten%20aircraft%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20audit%20by%20an%20FAA%20advisory%20panel%20released%20in%20February%20pointed%20to%20significant%20shortcomings%20in%20Boeing's%20safety%20culture%2C%20describing%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisconnect%26quot%3B%20between%20senior%20company%20management%20and%20other%20Boeing%20employees%20and%20skepticism%20that%20safety%20complaints%20by%20workers%20would%20not%20result%20in%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20message%20to%20employees%2C%20Stocker%20praised%20the%20employee%20for%20coming%20up%2C%20saying%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bwill%20use%20this%20moment%20to%20celebrate%20him%2C%20and%20to%20remind%20us%20all%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20behavior%20we%20will%20and%20will%20not%20accept%20as%20a%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoard%20under%20scrutiny%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESafety%20experts%20have%20said%20the%20problems%20at%20Boeing%20suggest%20significant%20safety%20culture%20defects%20that%20will%20not%20be%20turned%20around%20quickly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndustry%20watchers%20are%20waiting%20for%20more%20clues%20about%20future%20leadership%20of%20Boeing%20after%20Chief%20Executive%20Dave%20Calhoun%20said%20he%20will%20step%20down%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlass%20Lewis%2C%20the%20proxy%20advisory%2