get%20reservations.%20All%20I'm%20saying%20is%20that%20religion%20cannot%20be%20the%20basis%20of%20providing%20reservation.%20Poor%20in%20the%20country%20include%20all%20Hindus%2C%20Christians%2C%20and%20Parsis%3B%20all%20should%20get%20the%20benefits%20of%20reservations.%20Dalits%20and%20tribals%20for%20long%20have%20faced%20injustice%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20special%20reason%20that%20the%20makers%20of%20our%20constitution%20have%20taken%20the%20right%20decision%2C%20and%20we%20are%20grateful%20for%20that.%20No%20political%20party%20opposes%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20dangers%20associated%20with%20allowing%20reservations%20based%20on%20religion%20to%20Muslims%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20maker%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20after%20a%20lengthy%20discussion%20during%20its%20drafting%2C%20decided%20that%20reservation%20based%20on%20religion%20would%20be%20detrimental%20to%20society%20and%20would%20not%20be%20good%20for%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-not-allow-anyone-to-play-with-the-constitution-says-pm-modi-5596307%5C%22%3EWill%20Not%20Allow%20Anyone%20To%20Play%20With%20The%20Constitution%2C%20Says%20PM%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20Constitution%20was%20written%20at%20that%20time%2C%20leaders%20like%20Pandit%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%20and%20Rajendra%20Babu%20were%20all%20there%3B%20there%20was%20no%20one%20from%20the%20RSS%20or%20BJP%20and%20there%20were%20also%20representatives%20from%20all%20communities.%20After%20a%20lengthy%20discussion%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20reservation%20based%20on%20religion%20would%20be%20detrimental%20to%20society%20and%20would%20not%20be%20good%20for%20the%20long%20term.%20Social%20evils%20were%20faced%20by%20communities%20of%20tribals%20and%20Dalits%20for%20years.%20Untouchability%20and%20discrimination%20took%20place.%20Injustice%20was%20done%20to%20a%20very%20large%20section%20of%20society%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20birth.%20It%20was%20necessary%20to%20undo%20the%20wrongs%2C%20and%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20this%20was%20done%20by%20Sanatanis%2C%20apart%20from%20Nehru%20ji%2C%20who%20may%20think%20of%20himself%20above%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20assured%20that%20the%20Muslims%20will%20benefit%20equally%20from%20the%20central%20schemes%20if%20his%20government%20is%20voted%20into%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...we%20need%20to%20atone%20the%20sins%20and%20give%20reservations%20to%20those%20who%20deserve.%20I%20am%20also%20connected%20to%20the%20same%20sentiments.%20I%20want%20to%20live%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20I%20want%20to%20raise%20the%20prestige%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20I%20have%20been%20saying%20from%20Day%201%20that%20reservations%20based%20on%20religion%20go%20against%20the%20Constitution%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20Muslims%20won't%20get%20the%20benefit.%20We%20raised%20in%20Parliament%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20the%20poor%20in%20the%20general%20category%3B%20there%20was%20no%20objection%2C%20nobody%20fought%2C%20and%20no%20loot%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-give-you-modi-guarantee-will-not-let-reservations-end-amit-shah-5596085%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BI%20Give%20You%20Modi%20Guarantee%2C%20Will%20Not%20Let%20Reservations%20End%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20also%20said%20that%20he%20is%20committed%20to%20completing%20all%20government%20schemes%20in%20which%20every%20community%20and%20religion%20will%20be%20covered%20marking%20the%20fulfilment%20of%20his%20'guarantee%20of%20social%20justice%2C%20a%20guarantee%20of%20secularism'.