%20heard%20about%20extra-marital%20affairs%2C%20seedy%20%26quot%3Bcatch%20and%20kill%26quot%3B%20machinations%2C%20and%20the%20frantic%20damage%20control%20within%20his%20campaign%20ahead%20of%20the%202016%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20they%20heard%20a%20lot%20about%20accounting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20spent%20the%20day%20presenting%20two%20dry%20%E2%80%94%20but%20crucial%20%E2%80%94%20witnesses%20who%20handled%20The%20Trump%20Organization's%20finances%2C%20cutting%20checks%20and%20creating%20records%20within%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20witnesses%2C%20longtime%20Trump%20Organization%20employees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-mcconney-trump-organization-investigation-witness-allen-weisselberg-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJeffrey%20McConney%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Deborah%20Tarassoff%2C%20handled%20the%20checks%2C%20invoices%2C%20and%20other%20records%20that%20comprise%20the%2034%20business%20records%20the%20Manhattan%20district%20attorney's%20office%20alleges%20Trump%20illegally%20falsified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20paperwork%2C%20shown%20on%20giant%20TV%20screens%20in%20the%20courtroom%2C%20is%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20those%20falsifications%2C%20prosecutors%20say%2C%20was%20to%20cover%20up%20reimbursements%20to%20Michael%20Cohen%2C%20who%20wired%20a%20%24130%2C000%20hush-money%20payment%20to%20porn%20actress%20Stormy%20Daniels%20just%2011%20days%20before%20the%202016%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Attorney%20Alvin%20Bragg%20alleges%20the%20money%20interfered%20with%20the%20election%20by%20silencing%20Daniels'%20story%2C%20long%20denied%20by%20Trump%2C%20of%20a%20hotel-suite%20fling%20during%20a%20Lake%20Tahoe%20celebrity%20golf%20tournament%20in%202006%2C%20just%20months%20after%20Melania%20Trump%20gave%20birth%20to%20their%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20brief%20hearing%20Monday%20morning%20%E2%80%94%20in%20which%2