oses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20her%20out%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20Dr%20Alam%20shouts%20out%20instructions%20to%20someone%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20move%20fast.%E2%80%9D%20A%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20the%20roaring%20of%20an%20engine%20is%20indicative%20of%20a%20boat%20preparing%20to%20head%20to%20its%20next%20destination.%20As%20the%20white%20vessel%20powers%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F305137%2Fneelanjan-chakravarty-from-kolkata-builds-homestay-in-sunderbans-west-bengal-travel-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaters%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%3C%2Fa%3E%20(one%20of%20the%20largest%20mangrove%20forests%20in%20the%20world%20located%20in%20West%20Bengal)%2C%20the%20team%20inside%20%E2%80%94%20the%20doctor%2C%20a%20nurse%2C%20an%20x-ray%20technician%2C%20a%20lab%20technician%2C%20a%20pharmacist%20%E2%80%94%20busy%20themselves%20keeping%20medicines%20and%20equipment%20handy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20unique%20concept%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20month%2C%20we%20treat%2034%2C578%20patients%20in%20total%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Alam%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20shying%20away%20from%20taking%20credit%20for%20this%20massive%20volume.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20four%20boats%20in%20total%20and%20the%20schedule%20for%20each%20is%20set%20every%20Monday.%20Throughout%20the%20week%2C%20we%20travel%20across%20the%2030%20islands%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%2C%20covering%20six%20blocks%20in%20the%20North%20and%2013%20in%20the%20South.%20On%20Sundays%2C%20we%20return%20to%20the%20mainland%20where%20we%20stock%20up%20on%20supplies%2C%20medicines%2C%20rest%20and%20recharge%20for%20the%20next%20week.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Alam%20has%20been%20doing%20this%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20doctors%20to%20be%20appointed%20by%20the%20couple%20Mohammed%20Abdul%20Wohab%20and%