the%20weeks%2C%20people%20from%20across%20Sundarban%20islands%20would%20come%20to%20get%20an%20antidote%20to%20tuberculosis%2C%20cold%2C%20cough%20and%20fever.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-23-at-10.53.09-AM-1714724989.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Abdul%20Wohab%20and%20Sabitri%20Pal%2C%20the%20founders%20of%20SHIS%20Foundation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-23-at-10.53.09-AM-1714724989.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-23-at-10.53.09-AM-1714724989-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-23-at-10.53.09-AM-1714724989-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-23-at-10.53.09-AM-1714724989-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-23-at-10.53.09-AM-1714724989-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348888%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Abdul%20Wohab%20and%20Sabitri%20Pal%2C%20the%20founders%20of%20SHIS%20Foundation%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wohab%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20the%20patient%20numbers%20began%20to%20surge%20to%20an%20overwhelming%20peak%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20faced%20with%20the%20challenge%20of%20switching%20gears%20yet%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20time%20that%20French%20writer%2C%20Dominique%20Lapierre%2C%20was%20documenting%20the%20life%20of%20Gaston%20for%20his%20upcoming%20novel