looking%20out%20for%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECancer%20warrants%20a%20certain%20trepidation%2C%20a%20certain%20tiptoeing%2C%20a%20certain%20foreboding.%20But%20the%20laughter%20and%20happy%20chatter%20at%20the%20Access%20Life%20centres%2C%20disagree.%20For%20anyone%20looking%20in%2C%20there%20is%20only%20hope%20to%20be%20found%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20donate%20to%20their%20cause%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accesslife.org%2Fdonation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714733955000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcancer-centre-1714468603.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348647%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ankeet%20Dave%20and%20Girish%20Nair%2C%20founders%20of%20Access%20Life%2C%20were%20deeply%20affected%20by%20the%20pain%20of%20infants%20undergoing%20chemotherapy.%20They%20started%20helping%20the%20patients%E2%80%99%20families%20with%20shelter%2C%20food%20and%20transport%20in%20major%20Indian%20cities.%20This%20is%20their%20story%20of%20empathy%20and%20hard%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348647%2Fcancer-shelter-in-india-access-life-ankeet-dave-girish-nair-children-paediatric-care-in-mumbai%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Identify%20Fake%20%E2%80%98Paneer%E2%80%99%20At%20Home%3F%203%20Simple%20Tests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20vegetarians%2C%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%20%3C%2Fem%3E(cottage%20cheese)%20is%20touted%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20best%20sources%20of%20protein%20and%20forms%20an%20important%20part%20of%20the%20daily%20diet.%20However%2C%20consumers%20are%20turning%20wary%20about%2