s%20to%20combat%20dehydration%2C%20particularly%20during%20summer.%20But%20distinguishing%20real%20ORS%20from%20energy%20drinks%20marketed%20as%20such%20remains%20crucial.%20%E2%80%98Food%20pharmer%E2%80%99%20Revant%20Himatsingka%20shares%20how%20you%20can%20check%20real%20vs%20fake%20ORS.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348631%2Fors-fake-or-real-oral-rehydration-solution-for-summer-dehydration-diarrhoea-revant-food-pharmer%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Why%20Wait%20For%20Someone%2C%20Go%20Solo%E2%80%99%3A%20Ex-Banker%20is%20Taking%20Indian%20Women%20on%20Trips%20Across%20The%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20trekkers%20scaling%20the%20tranquil%20Dzuko%20Valley%20set%20amidst%20the%20highlands%20of%20Nagaland%20were%20treated%20to%20a%20fascinating%20sight.%20A%20group%20of%20girls%20could%20be%20seen%20cheering%20one%20among%20them%20as%20she%20trudged%20on.%20Closer%20inspection%20would%20reveal%20that%20their%20encouragement%20was%20directed%20towards%20a%20woman%20with%20an%20injured%20knee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virgin%20landscape%20boasts%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Ftags%2Fbest-treks-in-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20challenging%20steep%20climb%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Meenakshi%20Singh%20was%20unsure%20whether%20her%20knee%20could%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20terrain.%20When%20she%20was%20inclined%20to%20back%20out%2C%20the%20girls%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20hear%20of%20it%3B%20amping%20her%20positivity%20with%20every%20step%20she%20took.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticulating%20this%20%E2%80%9Conce-in-a-lifetime%E2%80%9D%20experience%2C%20Meenakshi%20says%20the%20girls%20in%20her%20group%20never%20gave%20up%20on%20her.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20almost%20pulled%20me%20half-way!%20One%20of%20th